g threw personal-best 69.12 meters at the World Athletics Championships in Eugene, Oregon, beating Sandra Perkovic of Croatia and Valarie Allman of the U.S. to win the gold.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9884951462479101, \"rank\": 0.004456284512622916, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 784, \"end\": 790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.8518661085238248, \"rank\": 0.170729574847286, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}, {\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"score\": 0.9999603806702178, \"rank\": 3.809984669451018e-05, \"text\": \"Sandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\"}, {\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_men's_national_handball_team\", \"score\": 0.9989581610033453, \"rank\": 0.0010267151583422606, \"text\": \"Croatia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_men's_national_handball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_men's_national_handball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valarie_Allman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Valarie Allman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valarie_Allman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valarie_Allman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"Feng\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"personal-best 69.12 meters\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"Eugene\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her victory ended Chinese athletes' 11-year title drought in the women's discus throw event at the World Championships.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5562315145226584, \"rank\": 0.7973464154642222, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her victory\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's discus throw event\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt such a relief at that moment because I proved I could do it,\\\" Feng told China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9891150819015513, \"rank\": 0.011004670161830678, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Micha