1, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why she has been working hard on improving her flexibility and coordination, which can even match some short-distance hurdling athletes.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her flexibility\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"coordination\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"some short-distance hurdling athletes\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in a good form now,\\\" Feng said.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good form\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"Feng\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just focus on training and improving my performance.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"my performance\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as I can maintain regular practice, I will not perform badly in Paris.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999942758677, \"rank\": 5.724072391957586e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"regular practice\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My goal of the year is definitely to win the gold at the 2024 Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My goal\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u